grep -ri "claude\|anthropic" --include="*.java" --include="*.md" --include="*.yml" --include="*.dart" .
# If ANY results found: STOP and remove them
```

### 3. Commit Message Rules
- MUST NOT contain "Claude" or "Anthropic"
